Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model

Class StackManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.StackManager
  • public class StackManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a common point of access to all the decks of the game, that allows drawing and discarding of all the cards. The "original" complete decks (i.e. the full set of cards) are passed as constructor parameter.
